Local-Global 7-Network Parcellation of the Human Cerebral Cortex

Source: R/schaefer.R
schaefer7.Rd

Coordinate data for the Schaefer et al. (2018) cortical atlas, with 100-1000 regions on the cortical surface of the brain, aligned with 7 previously described functional networks (Yeo et al., 2011).

data(schaefer7_100)
